metadata.name: Yaw Wen
metadata.description:
Digital drawing, 2022, 3340 x 4724 px, 13.173.728 Bytes, 300 dpi

“We keep moving forward, opening new doors, and doing new things, because we’re curious and curiosity keeps leading us down new paths.”

- Walt Disney

This work is something completely new for me. At first I felt a little uncomfortable, but now I really like the style. I tried to create a manga/anime character, as I really appreciate the illustrations in this art genre. I wanted the work to be clearly recognizable as manga, but I still wanted to keep as much of my sketchy style as possible. I managed to do that quite nicely, I think. Maybe there will be more in this direction in the future.

Flo
